nhc_headline: ...JULIETTE MOVING NORTH-NORTHWESTWARD INTO HOSTILE ENVIRONMENTAL CONDITIONS OF THE EASTERN NORTH PACIFIC...
summary: ...JULIETTE MOVING NORTH-NORTHWESTWARD INTO HOSTILE ENVIRONMENTAL CONDITIONS OF THE EASTERN NORTH PACIFIC... As of 8:00 AM PDT Wed Aug 27 the center of Juliette was located near 23.0, -119.5 with movement NNW at 13 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1001 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
